    "how_to_add_a_new_category": [
      "1. Go to https://quizapi.io/quizzes/templates — find the new template",
      "2. The TAGS shown below the template card (e.g. 'redis', 'k8s') — use the first one as 'tag'",
      "3. Copy any existing entry below and change the values",
      "4. Fields explained:",
      "   id    → unique key, lowercase, no spaces (e.g. 'redis')",
      "   tag   → tag shown on QuizAPI template card — MUST match exactly (e.g. 'redis')",
      "   label → display name shown on the quiz card (e.g. 'Redis')",
      "   icon  → any emoji (e.g. '🔴')",
      "   color → hex color for the card glow (e.g. '#dc2626')",
      "   group → section heading — use one of: 'DevOps & Cloud' | 'Programming' | 'Database & General'",
      "5. Commit the file — quiz updates automatically, no code changes needed"
    ]
  },
